    "Tap + in the bottom bar to start a new task and type a title." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "点击底部栏的 + 开始新任务并输入标题。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Tap a day on the calendar to set the date; tap it again to clear." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "点击日历上的日期即可设置日期；再次点击可清除。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Tap a group's ··· menu on the board to rename, recolor, or delete it. Inside a task, tap Status to add a new group or drag any tile onto the trash bar to delete one." : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "点击看板上分组的 ··· 菜单可重命名、改色或删除该分组。在任务中点击\"状态\"可新增分组，或将任意分组拖到垃圾桶处删除。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Tap a group's ··· menu on the board to rename, recolor, or delete it. Inside a task, tap Status to add a new group, drag-reorder rows, or expand the sheet and use Delete a Status." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "在看板上点击分组的 ··· 菜单可重命名、改色或删除。在任务中点击“状态”可新增分组、拖动行排序，或展开面板并使用“删除状态”。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Tap Add in the switcher to create a new board with placeholder text — then tap the title, subtitle, or icon on the board header to edit them in place." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "在切换器中点击“添加”创建带有占位文本的新看板，然后点击看板标题、副标题或图标即可直接编辑。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Tap Add to create your first tag." : {
      "comment" : "A message displayed when a user has not created any tags.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "点击\"添加\"创建您的第一个标签。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Tap any rendered line to jump back into edit mode and adjust the raw markdown. Drag the sheet down to dismiss the keyboard and return to the preview." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "点击任意已渲染的行可回到编辑模式并调整原始 Markdown。向下拖动面板可收起键盘并返回预览。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Tap the archive button in the bottom bar to open the board switcher. Fresh installs ship with three boards — Personal, Study, and Work — each with their own groups, tags, and tasks." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "点击底部栏的归档按钮打开看板切换器。全新安装会提供三个看板——个人、学习和工作——每个看板都有自己的分组、标签和任务。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Tap the Notes area on a task to type. Markdown is supported — **bold**, *italic*, # heading, and - bullet lines all render once you tap away." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "点击任务中的笔记区域即可输入。支持 Markdown：**粗体**、*斜体*、# 标题和 - 项目符号会在你点开后渲染。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Tap the search field in the bottom bar; the bar transforms and the keyboard appears." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "点击底部栏中的搜索框；底栏会切换形态并弹出键盘。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Tap to check" : {
      "comment" : "Default value for a settings row before the user calculates local storage usage.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "点击检查"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Tap X on the bar to clear the query and return to the board." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "点击栏上的 X 可清除搜索并返回看板。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Task asks for notification permission only to deliver local reminders you opt into per task." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Task 只会为了发送你为任务开启的本地提醒而请求通知权限。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Task couldn't open its on-device database, so your changes this session won't be saved. Please export your data from Settings → Data → Manual Control and restart the app." : {
      "comment" : "A warning that a user's data is not being saved.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Task 无法打开本机数据库，本次会话的更改将不会保存。请前往 设置 → 数据 → 手动控制 导出数据，然后重新启动应用。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Task does not bundle advertising, analytics, or tracking SDKs." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Task 不包含广告、分析或跟踪 SDK。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Task does not make any network requests on its own." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Task 本身不会发起任何网络请求。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Task does not provide professional advice, project management guarantees, or compliance services." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Task 不提供专业建议、项目管理保证或合规服务。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Task is a personal productivity app for tracking your own tasks and reminders." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Task 是一款用于跟踪个人任务和提醒的效率应用。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Task is a personal productivity app inspired by Notion's Kanban view. Design language adapted from Coin and Body." : {
      "comment" : "A description of the app.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Task 是一款个人效率应用，灵感来自 Notion 的看板视图。设计语言改编自 Coin 和 Body。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Task reminder" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "任务提醒"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Teal" : {
      "comment" : "Name of the accent color teal.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "青蓝"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Text Size" : {
      "comment" : "A button that dismisses the sheet.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "文字大小"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Text Size scales fonts across the whole app while respecting Dynamic Type." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "文字大小会缩放整个应用中的字体，同时尊重动态字体设置。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The board header keeps quick controls for Card Order and the date filter. Default Status now lives in each status column's ··· menu." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "看板标题区保留了卡片排序和日期筛选的快捷控制。默认状态现在位于每个状态列的 ··· 菜单中。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The widget reads a small JSON snapshot of upcoming tasks from the App Group container shared with the main app." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "小组件会从与主应用共享的 App Group 容器读取一份较小的即将到来的任务 JSON 快照。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Theme" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "主题"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "This status will be removed. Its tasks will move to the first remaining status." : {
      "comment" : "Message shown in GroupMenuSheet when confirming deletion of a status.",
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "此状态将被移除。其中的任务将移至第一个剩余状态。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "This task and any reminder you set will be removed permanently." : {
      "comment" : "Message shown when confirming deletion of a task.",
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "此任务及其设置的提醒将被永久删除。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "This will delete every board, group, tag, and task on this device, then restore the three default boards (Personal, Study, Work) with five groups each. This can't be undone." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "这将删除本机上的所有看板、分组、标签和任务，然后恢复三个默认看板（Personal、Study、Work），每个包含五个分组。此操作无法撤销。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Title" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "标题"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Today" : {
      "comment" : "A button that jumps to today's date.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "今天"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Toggle Checkbox in a task to show a box before the card title. Tap the box on the card to mark the task done or not done without moving it to another status." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "在任务中打开“复选框”，可在卡片标题前显示方框。点击卡片上的方框即可标记完成或未完成，而不必移动到其他状态。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Toggle Reminder to schedule a local notification. A small footer on the card shows a notes icon when the task has notes and an alarm icon when a reminder is set." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "打开“提醒”即可安排本地通知。卡片底部的小区域会在任务有笔记时显示笔记图标，在设置提醒时显示闹钟图标。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Two boards can each have their own group called \"Doing\" — groups and tags don't cross boards." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "两个看板可以各自拥有名为“Doing”的分组——分组和标签不会跨看板共享。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Type 9:30 as 930" : {
      "comment" : "A hint for the user on how to format a time.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "将 9:30 输入为 930"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Type 21:30 as 2130" : {
      "comment" : "A hint for the user on how to format a time.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "将 21:30 输入为 2130"
          }
        }
      }
    },
